node ER · ER · ⟦Maliketh, the Black Blade:ER:9b48cd⟧

WHO   — Maliketh, the Black Blade — the shadow-beast who keeps Death
WHAT  — Marika's shadowbound beast and half-brother, the keeper into whose blade Destined Death was sealed
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: Farum Azula and the Bestial Sanctum — the hidden places where Death is kept  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — To mend the Ring, the Tarnished must slay him in Farum Azula and loose Death upon the world
HOW   — Guards his single charge absolutely; after part of Death was stolen, he hides as the cleric-beast Gurranq, devouring deathroot to take back what leaked

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  The faithful guardian whose success would have made the story impossible.

